product.title: Cute Micro Jiguang Street | LIMITED STOCK
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • Open your door to the world of ancient buildings with the Jiguang Street set

    Join the Little Micro World in Jiguang Street, one of the oldest shopping streets in Taichung. You will find unique and delicious street food that could not be found elsewhere

    🌸 Measurements: varies for each sets
    🌸 Not compatible with leading blocks of standard size (16mm) 
    🌸 This is Micro blocks (12mm)
    🌸 Each set has over 620 micro pieces and varies for each sets
    🌸 Includes 2 mini dolls for each set
    📦 Excludes original box to protect the environment. For further details please see below.*

    We have picked 4 Micro Cute Micro Jiguang Street for you to build from scratch, role play, and learn how to run a Taiwanese street food market in your own room. 


    Our first Cute Micro Jiguang Street sells Wanbo Tea Shop. Taiwan tea includes four main types: oolong tea, black tea, green tea and white tea, everything you need to start your own tea ceremony. With the exquisite details as shown. It contains attractive 630 pieces. 

    Our second Cute Micro Jiguang Street is Akua Hot Pot 火鍋,  is a simple dish in which a pot of heated broth is placed in the centre of a communal table for diners to toss in various uncooked meat, seafood, and vegetables. With the exquisite details as shown. It contains flaming hot 620 pieces. 

    Our third Cute Micro Jiguang Street is Boboi Boutique selling their popular dress made from satin and silk fabrics, festival-mood colors, and intricate embroidery. It contains 635 pieces.

     

    Our forth Cute Micro Jiguang Street is Casino or Taiwanese Mahjong, which is the most famous tile game in Taiwanese. Play it with your family or friends and everyone will be excited store. It contains delicious 625 pieces.

     

     

    Measurements: about 4in/11cm x 2.5in /6cm  (allow up to 5cm variations in different sets)

    Start building your street today by following the instruction booklet.

    STOCK NOTICE: Wanbo Tea Shop variant out of stock - we apologise for any inconvenience caused.

    The perfect gift for those who love their crafts!

    You will love seeing your family and friends in excitement when they receive our micro building blocks, leaving an everlasting smile on your loved ones by surprising them with these super innovative and cool building blocks today.

    Micro Blocks: Smaller than the traditional building block.


    * Our Building Block sets are packaged in safe and secured protective bags. They do NOT come in the original box to reduce the carbon footprint, save the planet and reduce postage cost on your behalf. It will come with all the pieces and a detailed instruction booklet for you to follow. 

    Features

    🌸 100% premium quality (ABS) plastic
    ☕ Sharp brilliant colors and solid feel
    🌸 Challenging and rewarding to stimulate all brains
    🥣 High-quality durable non-toxic green material

    WARNING: CHOKING HAZARD - Contains small parts; not suitable for children under 6 years old unless there is adult supervision.


  • Do you ship worldwide? Yes, we ship to over 300 countries and are proud to provide free shipping to the United States, the United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, and many countries in Europe.

    What are the blocks made from?     All our building blocks are manufactured from a High-Quality Premium strong, resilient plastic known as acrylonitrile butadiene styrene (ABS) and will stand the test of time and provide hours of fun building their own creations

    Does this help with stress and development?     Our building blocks are a great way to relieve stress and engage in meaningful and joyful conversations. As children comment on their building creations, they develop important communication skills including the ability to explain ideas, describe their work, talk about the process and verbalize challenges that they had along the way. 

    CHOKING HAZARD: Small parts. Not for children under 6 years old

     

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: 5-20 Business days
